text.0: A bogus story spreading on social media uses a doctored image of an indictment to falsely claim George Soros has been arrested in the U.S. "for election interference." The actual charges are against six Russian nationals for cyberattacks. https://t.co/zk4rl2IbDk #FactCHAT
text.1: Back in 2016, Donald Trump wrongly called his victory a "landslide." Now, some are taking a page out of Trump's book to claim Biden won in a landslide. He didn't, either. https://t.co/dXRTWZIHnM #FactCHAT
